data.description: Welcome to this investors dream! Situated on a large level lot slightly over 1/2 an acre, here's your opportunity to finish a beautiful brick home in St. Louis County. Newer electrical, plumbing and HVAC makes this home enticing to say the least. Upon entry, you are greeted by newer flooring and open space. The living area is graced with a woodburning fireplace. The first of two primary suites sits right off the living room and features a spacious primary bath that includes plumbing for double vanities, large shower and walk-in closet. The kitchen includes newer cabinets and counters. The second bedroom is off the kitchen and features a double closet and adjacent to the 2nd full bathroom. The second primary suite is privately situated adjacent to the two car garage and features a finished full bathroom and tons of living space. The laundry room is spacious and includes entry to the mechanical room. A wonderful opportunity to finish this wonderful home on a picturesque street.
